Healthcare Communication
Reimagined

Leveraging the latest advancements in AI to increase profitability, improve clinician capacity, and strengthen brand

Developed in Collaboration

with experts from leading health systems

Increase Clinician Capacity

Empower clinicians and staff to communicate in a way that’s easy for patients and families to understand, without any extra work.

Increase Your Profitability

The non-English-speaking patient population is growing. Serve a larger market with the first HIPAA-compliant AI-driven interpreter & translator.

Strengthen Your Brand

Extend your reach to patients’ loved ones throughout the full continuum of care — whether they are 10 miles or 10,000 miles away — fully automated.
